' Version:       1.3.3
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
'
' (*) 1. Self-Subclassing UserControl template (IDE safe) by Paul Caton:
'
'        Self-subclassing Controls/Forms - NO dependencies (v1.1.0010 2004.10.07)
'        http://www.planet-source-code.com/vb/scripts/ShowCode.asp?txtCodeId=54117&lngWId=1
'
'     2. MouseLeave()/MouseEnter() code by Paul Caton.
'
'     3. Some TreeView macros by MH (adapted from AllApiDemo project).
'
'     4. OLE Drag & Drop code based on vbAccelerator vbalTreeView.ctl
'
'        vbAccelerator TreeView Control
'        http://www.vbaccelerator.com/home/VB/Code/Controls/TreeView/TreeView_Control/VB6_TreeView_Full_Source_zip_vbalTreeView_ctl.asp
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
'
' History:
'
'   * 1.0.0: - First release.
'
'   * 1.1.0: - Added  <hNode-Key> 'dummy-collection', getting:
'              - Faster Key check (collection built-in).
'              - Faster hNode 'extraction' from Key (collection built-in).
'
'              Private <hNode-Key> array lets extract directly node Key, as well as
'              operate over node's lParam member.
'              Also hNode (array) is used as 'delete' flag in TVN_DELETEITEM notification.
'              This flag will be used for 'removing/compacting' both collection and array
'              on deleting node(s) (see DeleteNode() function).
'
'              Array could be used to store extra node information for processing in a
'              custom-draw routine (hNode->lParam-> node array index ...).
'
'   * 1.2.0: - Added HoldDeletePostProcess() sub. (See sub's note!).
'            - Added SelectionChanged() event.
'            - Added hWnd property (hWndTreeView).
'            - Added HitTest() method.
'            - Added NodeFirstVisible() and NodeLastVisible() props.
'            - Added b[ExpandChildren] option (Expand() sub).
'            - Added b[CollapseChildren] option (Collapse() sub).
'            - Added b[SortAllLevels] option (SortChildren() sub).
'
'   * 1.3.0: - Added SetInsertionMark() method.
'            - Added SetHilitedNode() method. (*)
'              (*) This will interfere in NodeHilited() prop.
'                  Use NodeHilited() prop. for multil-select implementation.
'            - Added InsertMarkColor() prop.
'            - Added NodeLevel() prop.
'            - Added NodeTag() prop. (*)
'              (*) OLE Drag & Drop implementation can complicate copy/move of
'                  nodes due to oneness of keys. This lets store extra info for each
'                  node: You can generate 'auto-increased' keys and store meaningful
'                  information into node Tag.
'                  You can Set/Get manualy Tag through NodeTag() prop., or initialize
'                  it through AddNode() method (last opt. parameter).
'            - OLE Drag & Drop support:
'              > Added: OLEDragMode() prop.
'              > Added: OLEDropMode() prop.
'              > Added: OLEDragInsertStyle() prop.
'              > Added: OLEDragAutoExpand() prop.
'              > Added: OLEIsMyFormat() method.
'              > Added: OLEGetDragInfo() method.
'              > Added: OLEGetDropInfo() method.
'              > Added: OLEStartDrag() event.
'              > Added: OLEGiveFeedback() event.
'              > Added: OLEDragOver() event.
'              > Added: OLEDragDrop() event.
'              > Added: OLECompleteDrag() event.
'
'              More info:
'              http://www.devx.com/vb/Article/7864/1954?pf=true
'
'   * 1.3.1: - Forgotten:
'              - Added NodeExpanded() and NodeExpandedOnce() props.
'
'   * 1.3.2: - Added: CheckChildren() method (hereditary checking).
'            - Fixed: NodeDblClick not raised when DblClick on 'CheckBox'.
'                     Also node not expanded/collapsed.
'
'   * 1.3.3: - Added: Unicode support ?.
'----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
'
' Known issues:
'
'   *
